name: One Day At The Farmers Market Selling Jam
name_original: One Day At The Farmers Market Selling Jam
description: This game was made for the Kindred Game Jam Community. The theme was: Jam. (Hahaha. Very Cute theme guys.) You play as a charecter at the market selling jam. You must replenish the jam by pressing space. You also use arrow keys. Use space to also shoot.
